Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種東西和我們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…哪裡不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是說啦 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個是那個 這個是這個
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}OP
