Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.52,0:02:10.48,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,480)}#07 那個是那個、這個是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:10.48,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,480)\3c&HF2C855&\bord8}#07 那個是那個、這個是這個
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 坐在後面的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請把考卷收上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}期末考終於結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這次的有點難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不想補考呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}過去的事情就忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天就開個解放會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天放學以後要不要再來學生會室喝茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.96,EX,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塔（tart）：\N是一種焗烤食品，屬於西式餡餅的一個種類，特徵是餡料外露。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有美味的塔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塔…塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們的書記做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊啦 末續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前的資料我準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真快呢 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}考試期間是不是有點難為你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒 如果能幫上會長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是隔壁班的末續木葉醬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是剛才紅緒姐說的學生會的書記哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}據說很溫柔頭腦也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那態度是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊呀呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼會長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜拜 末續同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再來玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}超級火大！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是在剛搬來這個鎮上的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是有什麼煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…窩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊不…我剛來這個鎮上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不認識路不小心迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道你家住在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不介意的話我送你回去吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那之後我為了和紅緒大人進入同一所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從制服找到學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後努力學習漂亮地合格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅能和我進同一所學校真的很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}沒聽說過她有妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且那胸部…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明我那麼想成為紅緒大人的妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 退一百步來說妹妹也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是那個突然冒出來的小不點算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}整天對著紅緒大人賣萌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}超礙眼的啊！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小小小小 小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛…剛才那裡確實有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難 難道是宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}靈異現象？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你・說・誰…是妖怪啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼啦 一副可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小心我拍成照片放到新聞上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是真的啦 就是有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\move(642,666,640,710,835,1500)}那傢伙就算是紅緒大人的親戚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直被寵著你不覺得很狡猾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 紅緒的妹妹和親戚家的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特別是那個小矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為是個孩子就被疼愛真是不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我就去調查一下她們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想知道她們是什麼樣的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是新聞部的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說不定這個能成為有趣的報導
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用做到那種程度吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個形象奇怪的東西一定是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…就找找能掌握的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我去悄悄調查個清楚
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 校刊的採訪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:06:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想做一個紅緒大人的妹妹・小紅的特別專欄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃…這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟姐姐大人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會很沒意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可是紅緒大人的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家很感興…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\move(642,665,640,710,350,650)}是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種事…我很為難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才應該道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不自覺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那這次就只做資料介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 調查問卷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要填哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學生會長的妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}討厭被拿來做比較嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是不擅長做引人注目的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且這會讓大家失望的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒 這種事經常會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經習慣了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}洗澡時會從哪裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪裡最怕癢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}連這麼奇怪的問題都有！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一氣之下拜託別人做了很奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然說要偷偷調查
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幹什麼呀 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白和紅緒大人關係很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們是什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 如果有弱點的話要告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要說什什什麼關係的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼關係都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是你們關係很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一點都不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事情鬧大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是你指使的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用再來做書記了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請您原諒 紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管誰從什麼角度看都沒有什麼關係好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}仁子同學不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個人怎麼回事嘛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然還是不要調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會很順利的就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的心意…心意我領了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}咦 為什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果被人知道是我拜託你調查的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係 保守秘密也是記者的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在停下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大野仁子的名號會哭泣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}機 機動力…真不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不用跟過來的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}廁所很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學校的廁所裡有個叫花子的人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有紅紙 藍紙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}停！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在這裡等著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直接取材加上隱秘取材
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好想拍小紅的素顏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬真的可以不用調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會很順利的就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是不用了 求你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對了 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉說出來之前我都沒有發覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白醬還是個小孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小孩子上高中卻沒有人覺得不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這也有調查的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}記者之魂燃起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從一年級開始就不停寫報導
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}將來新聞部部長的位置就屬於我大野仁子了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}不 那個…雖然你的决心很值得敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 幹嘛 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要為難小紅和真白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼你會知道我想要報導她們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 好不容易拍到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不知道怎麼刪除嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之不要再給小紅添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那傢伙怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過照片沒事就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊咧 刪掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個小不點的…哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道對那傢伙一見鍾情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人家喜歡的是紅緒大人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在來發之前的期末考卷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}30分以下的要補考
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為啥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜雖然擅長背誦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是不擅長應用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好極端啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅來輔導白夜學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 我數學也不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也很不擅長現在教的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一起輔導吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 這裡要用這個公式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個問題要把5放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}7放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唔啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果遇到裂口女要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我記得她怕髮蠟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不愧是紅緒大人的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像很聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人今天也很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是剛才一直在嘆氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是因為累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好累沒幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}營養…妹妹成分不足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好想讓可愛的妹妹坐在膝蓋上然後工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬發來的郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去一下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}花子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用擔心花子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放學後的學校好恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺有什麼會冒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡要閉著眼睛衝過去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇啊 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藏在廁所裡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秒進秒出的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 真是危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然就跑起來了弄得側腹好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 出現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怪 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要胡說！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫人家怪物算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼能對著窩這樣的可愛女孩子說怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有人看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}偏偏這個時候…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然學校的廁所危險又不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}確實很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學校的廁所很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以以後去廁所的時候跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會陪你去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣才危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學生會不是有個書記嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說末續啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}長女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總覺得沒有一點妹妹的感覺結果是長女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個我沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}認真的老實的孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該說這樣才像是女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有時候會做點心帶來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然比不上小紅的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不對…比不上小紅的手藝才對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要開始補考了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請加油吧 FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概…因為小紅教過我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概 一定 有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說起來 白夜要補考 真白卻沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對我來說太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}耍詐剛好達到及格邊緣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}耍詐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微用了點暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我混進學校就是用這個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以真白來上高中誰也不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然有那種力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜也能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是耍詐不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和真白不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是高一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}進學生會室好艱難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}討厭 在樓道大喊大叫真是沒品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經不想呼吸同樣的空氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且居然是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是拿她沒輒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果變成這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼面對紅緒大人才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉呀 末續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊呀 副會長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不…會長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去和妹妹接觸充電去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜託給我加滿油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很快就會回來了吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}春天還很遙遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到了三月就會暖和了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想去洗手間…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思你去把紅緒找來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概會和小紅她們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和妹妹一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果遇到的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會帶你去廁所的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼總在這種時候讓窩撞見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}窩也想牽著手去廁所！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 補考結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是不快點回去的話撫子會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是紅緒大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學生會還有工作所以留下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道散發著毒氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}神經毒素嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定沒錯 很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要趕快把紅緒隔離起來才行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}隔離？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要獨占我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}貪・心・的・孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是有多樂觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被真白碳表揚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是沒法理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐是很有人氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這樣的態度會被狂熱的粉絲們討厭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}簡直不可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然對紅緒大人那種態度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然對紅緒大人那種態度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓我們以世界和平為主題進行討論吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要 請你不要跟我搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全校學生…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不對 是全世界的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明他們的幸福才是我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是對著窩說那種話的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}窩真的不知道該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續同學 你有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都已經這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有話要對三峰同學說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是說你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在嗎喂！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我嗎 有啥事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然憑著氣勢的說了出來…怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你難道說是從山的那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種事…怎麼樣都無所謂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我聞出味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我像村裡來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像村姑？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底啥事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…我是希望你不要對紅緒大人那樣無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 這個…也就是說…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先把話說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無禮的可是紅緒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你直接叫名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給我買奇怪的睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還給我買奇怪的內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還想跟著我去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還想帶我一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還在情人節那天買了特大的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你竟然炫耀…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒紅緒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你至少加個姐吧 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笨？！說別人笨蛋的人才是笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被說是笨蛋然後說別人笨蛋的人才是笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是說別人笨蛋的人才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是幾歲小孩的吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被說是笨蛋的人才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想哭的可是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續原來是這樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像被紅緒的毒氣毒害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作為同族真是太丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個人跟我們是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我聞到了同族的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是說末續也可以變成什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我倒是注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼不說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得無所謂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不對 有所謂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡應該感興趣吧 至少是同族
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臭小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}高中出道有錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}方言都冒出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬你幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為了尋找大新聞就爬到這上面來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是好像也沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟真白醬吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還不是瞧不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還跟我炫耀她跟紅緒大人一起洗澡的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為啥小不點那麼小還是高中生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道你是從山那邊來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她難道是我的同族？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是混進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要真是這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎麼了 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了 冷靜點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太失禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我做了什麼錯事嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ED
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼下週的『未確認進行式』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}窩是木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}終於輪到窩出場啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下回是 紅緒大人的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人的中午
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三部分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下週見哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能治癒妹妹悲傷的、還是妹妹
Comment: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
